  <subsubsection|Version 1 - Prototype>

  <\verbatim>
    (func $ext_storage_changes_root_version_1

    (param $parent_hash i64) (return i64))
  </verbatim>

  \;

  <strong|Arguments>:

  <\itemize>
    <item><strong|><verbatim|parent_hash>: a pointer-size as defined in
